  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bbf ; \u0b85\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Money laundering in the name of bank; Police warn to be careful",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Aton and Norwood police have said that they have received information that some people are laundering money in the name of a private bank branch located in Aton and its neighboring plantation areas.",
        "The group going to the plantations of these areas took money from many people in Aton Klangan plantation saying that they are advancing bank loan and housing projects for plantation people with the financial assistance of France and for that they have to pay 2,245 rupees first.",
        "Some people who came to know that the name of the private bank was on the debit slip of the money received, directly met the manager of the said bank branch located in Atton. However, the bank manager denied this and immediately filed a complaint at the Attan Police Station.",
        "Complaints have also been made there as the plantation area in question falls under the Norwood Police Division. Informing about this, the private bank manager has asked the people of Perundo area to be aware of this improper collection of money being carried out using the name of his bank and if anyone visits, they should ask for information about them while taking pictures of the said persons on their mobile phones.",
        "At the same time, the police have asked to be vigilant about this and have asked them to report the movement of such persons to the nearest police station or to the emergency police number."
      ],
